http://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/Madhavans-Saala-Khadoos-moves-celebs-to-tears/article14016317.ece

Bollywood celebrities Shilpa Shetty Kundra and Dia Mirza got emotional after catching a special screening of the forthcoming sports drama Saala Khadoos in Mumbai. Directed by Sudha Kongara, Saala Khadoos is about a rustic fisherwoman, played by Ritika Singh, who is mentored by a boxing coach (played by R. Madhavan) to become a champion.Ritika too couldn’t hold back her tears at the screening held on Friday. “Everyone was crying, so even I got emotional,” she said.“Everyone was crying. Maddy (Madhavan) especially was outstanding,” said Shilpa.